*----------------------------------*
| Compute the local for SDF values |
*----------------------------------*

BE CAREFUL : Only for SDF VALUES
Remember that when we create noise, we keep the correspondance between the vertex of the mesh
and those of the noised mesh, but not between the voxels of the object and those of the voxelized
noised mesh.

Inputs : 2 SDF values files
-------

Output : a .TXT file which contains the sorted local error values
--------

To compile  :
-------------

g++ -Wall localError.cpp -p localError

To use :
--------

./localError path/to/the/first/values.txt path/to/the/second/values.txt
